Generate 3 SEO-compliant, academic-style titles for the following product:

Product Name: {{ product_name }}
Reference URL: {{ reference_url }}
{% if reference_content %}
Reference Page Content Summary: {{ reference_content[:2000] }}
Reference Page Title: {{ reference_title }}
{% endif %}
Language: {{ language }}

Requirements:
1. Length: 50-65 characters (English)
2. Structure: "Main Title: Subtitle" format
3. Must include: number word, power word, positive emotion word
4. Core keywords positioned in first half
5. Long-tail keywords in subtitle section
6. No promotional words like "recommended" or "best"
7. Base the titles on actual product information from the reference page content

Output each title on a separate line, without numbering or additional annotations.
